  "content": "\n                <p>Adenoid <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"d8aolm\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2565f5179622b57d8e166369a90801a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"aFXQg-\" data-sxid=\"aFXQg-\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBDZWxsdWxhciBhZGFwdGF0aW9u\" id=\"L576ddd4be62c37361d9c4a5086e6b126\" data-source=\"L576ddd4be62c37361d9c4a5086e6b126\">hypertrophy</span> is <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"W8aPlm\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7c2f7198db9b555525515960ad48bd59\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"aFXQg-\" data-sxid=\"aFXQg-\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBDZWxsdWxhciBhZGFwdGF0aW9u\" id=\"L19560a5fb5edaace17de89a3c4b11a04\" data-source=\"L19560a5fb5edaace17de89a3c4b11a04\">hyperplasia</span> of the <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zc0a24109065435d7e654750124207a1d\" data-learningcard-id=\"960NMS\" data-lxid=\"960NMS\" data-section-id=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-sxid=\"ZEcZ8V0\" data-title=\"THltcGhhdGljIHN5c3RlbSDihpIgU2Vjb25kYXJ5IGx5bXBoYXRpYyBvcmdhbnM=\" id=\"Lb0372bb770bf47f5182389457bfec034\" data-source=\"Lb0372bb770bf47f5182389457bfec034\">pharyngeal tonsils</span>. It only becomes symptomatic if it leads to congestion of the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NQ0-wf\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z93379c773fed1d12988535934bd7d0ce\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-lxid=\"ap0QLS\" data-section-id=\"Nvc-Ze0\" data-sxid=\"Nvc-Ze0\" data-title=\"QWlyd2F5cyBhbmQgbHVuZ3Mg4oaSIEdyb3NzIGFuYXRvbXk=\" id=\"Lc64b3199467a42fc8dfa3bce9fcc4400\" data-source=\"Lc64b3199467a42fc8dfa3bce9fcc4400\">choanae</span> and eustachian tubes. The condition is common in children with recurrent inflammation of the upper <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-lxid=\"ap0QLS\" data-title=\"QWlyd2F5cyBhbmQgbHVuZ3M=\" id=\"Le51647cc599427f71ec846b3be2e43cc\" data-source=\"Le51647cc599427f71ec846b3be2e43cc\">airways</span>. Clinical features include mouth breathing, snoring, hyponasal speech, and <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z32cfe444b37709abb656fd5dbfa182da\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dj01cT\" data-lxid=\"Dj01cT\" data-section-id=\"6kYjK6\" data-sxid=\"6kYjK6\" data-title=\"QWRlbm9pZCBoeXBlcnRyb3BoeSDihpIgQ2xpbmljYWwgZmVhdHVyZXM=\" id=\"L979718297a17858a941f4931a32f2427\" data-source=\"L979718297a17858a941f4931a32f2427\">adenoid facies</span>. Adenoid <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"d8aolm\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2565f5179622b57d8e166369a90801a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"aFXQg-\" data-sxid=\"aFXQg-\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBDZWxsdWxhciBhZGFwdGF0aW9u\" id=\"L2f85e1b43014dbb91469f54928d89f1e\" data-source=\"L2f85e1b43014dbb91469f54928d89f1e\">hypertrophy</span> is diagnosed using <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"94bNlF\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"L4baa57f7c7e39ad2aa00a677bab17729\" data-source=\"L4baa57f7c7e39ad2aa00a677bab17729\">flexible nasopharyngoscopy</span>, which should show enlarged adenoid tissue. An <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"QCbu7D\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zf3faaddeb9cf756c21d915c0634bbc86\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dj01cT\" data-lxid=\"Dj01cT\" data-section-id=\"7kY466\" data-sxid=\"7kY466\" data-title=\"QWRlbm9pZCBoeXBlcnRyb3BoeSDihpIgVHJlYXRtZW50\" id=\"Lf07be02380c4b55b0aa26eb1d6c4d37d\" data-source=\"Lf07be02380c4b55b0aa26eb1d6c4d37d\">adenotonsillectomy</span> is indicated in patients with chronic/<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"tZbXWH\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zaac4a294224f2b2a1acf64883f789cfd\" data-learningcard-id=\"sj0tbT\" data-lxid=\"sj0tbT\" data-section-id=\"R4YlQ6\" data-sxid=\"R4YlQ6\" data-title=\"U2ludXNpdGlzIOKGkiBEZWZpbml0aW9ucw==\" id=\"L518a8c6233b0bb3b1236095413424137\" data-source=\"L518a8c6233b0bb3b1236095413424137\">recurrent sinusitis</span>, chronic/recurrent otitis media, and/or symptomatic nasal obstruction.</p>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Common in children <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"VGhlIGFkZW5vaWRzIGFyZSBsYXJnZXN0IGluIGNoaWxkcmVuIDxzcGFuIGNsYXNzPSJub3dyYXAiPjLigJM2IHllYXJzPC9zcGFuPiBvZiBhZ2UuCg==\" id=\"E38ad9763dffb56319ed8b9ecc55569ff\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li>Very rare in adults <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Ec1502d3e1be06ad2aa7314b36a86556b\"></span></span> <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"6CXjGZ0\" data-page=\"269–74\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"1\">[1]</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\"><span class=\"merkspruch\"><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Adenoid <span class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"d8aolm\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z2565f5179622b57d8e166369a90801a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"aFXQg-\" data-sxid=\"aFXQg-\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBDZWxsdWxhciBhZGFwdGF0aW9u\" id=\"L577ee4ee694a7f231d652531bd34b018\" data-source=\"L577ee4ee694a7f231d652531bd34b018\">hypertrophy</span></span> is the most common cause of nasal obstruction in children.</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"unwichtig\">Epidemiological data refers to the US, unless otherwise specified.</span></p>\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li>Physiological</li>\n<li>Adenoidal inflammation due to<ul>\n<li>Viral or bacterial infections <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Ee0035fe098696915ebe5fe2c724ba6d3\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"dQcoEX0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zad7c6b008a82ef99e199a600fba0e223\" data-learningcard-id=\"ek0x5T\" data-lxid=\"ek0x5T\" data-section-id=\"fSck_b0\" data-sxid=\"fSck_b0\" data-title=\"SHlwZXJzZW5zaXRpdml0eSByZWFjdGlvbnMg4oaSIFR5cGUgSSBoeXBlcnNlbnNpdGl2aXR5IHJlYWN0aW9u\" id=\"L484372a8dd0acb65562783444ddc4587\" data-source=\"L484372a8dd0acb65562783444ddc4587\">Allergens</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"Y68b8add694ad1b801555c79c708b5e95\" class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\">Mechanical congestion of the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NQ0-wf\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z93379c773fed1d12988535934bd7d0ce\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-lxid=\"ap0QLS\" data-section-id=\"Nvc-Ze0\" data-sxid=\"Nvc-Ze0\" data-title=\"QWlyd2F5cyBhbmQgbHVuZ3Mg4oaSIEdyb3NzIGFuYXRvbXk=\" id=\"Lb0fa11b0a07fbc4e3a0b3e0f1cf5c4ef\" data-source=\"Lb0fa11b0a07fbc4e3a0b3e0f1cf5c4ef\">choanae</span>\n</h2>\n<ul class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\">\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Mouth breathing</span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> </span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"TmFzYWwgYnJlYXRoaW5nIGlzIGltcGFpcmVkLgo=\" id=\"E0e3e7e8ce8879df1eeffbe487ce9947f\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"wichtig\">Hyponasal speech</span></span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> </span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"VGhlIGFic2VuY2Ugb2YgbmFzYWwgYWlyZmxvdyBkdXJpbmcgc3BlZWNoLCByZXN1bHRpbmcgaW4gd2hhdCBpcyBjb21tb25seSBjYWxsZWQgYSDigJxuYXNhbCB2b2ljZeKAnS4K\" id=\"E7e692561c20deaa19ad7a9b8e37f751f\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"api\" data-type=\"anker\" id=\"Z32cfe444b37709abb656fd5dbfa182da\">Adenoid facies</span></span> <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"E0eb11e215f14f5fdb0f3a840c76c6c44\"></span></span><ul>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Elongated, <span class=\"wichtig\"><span class=\"nowrap\">open-mouthed</span></span> face, short upper lip,<span class=\"wichtig\"> thin nostrils</span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Malpositioned and prominent upper <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zc69fe2afeddb2ae579ee295cfaab71f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"jp0_6S\" data-lxid=\"jp0_6S\" data-section-id=\"Ro1lb30\" data-sxid=\"Ro1lb30\" data-title=\"T3JhbCBjYXZpdHkg4oaSIFRlZXRo\" id=\"L150fb682705a46b66ed11c6918537772\" data-source=\"L150fb682705a46b66ed11c6918537772\">teeth</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"24XTiy\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z8b886a5c6d6c17b40bcf17f556616561\" data-learningcard-id=\"vo0AdS\" data-lxid=\"vo0AdS\" data-section-id=\"f6ck4W0\" data-sxid=\"f6ck4W0\" data-title=\"RW1icnlvZ2VuZXNpcyDihpIgTW9ycGhvZ2VuZXNpcw==\" id=\"L1d4c4750dea1f14c888695fdbd060734\" data-source=\"L1d4c4750dea1f14c888695fdbd060734\">hypoplastic</span> upper <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zcd68913a944e4c1ef8247cdf61ca0d46\" data-learningcard-id=\"vK0ARS\" data-lxid=\"vK0ARS\" data-section-id=\"OscIEd0\" data-sxid=\"OscIEd0\" data-title=\"U2t1bGwg4oaSIEphdw==\" id=\"Lb7ac12f95cf058bf7e3c46bfa29dbb23\" data-source=\"Lb7ac12f95cf058bf7e3c46bfa29dbb23\">jaw</span>, <span class=\"nowrap\">high-arched</span> <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"StXy1-\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z281012acfe74769bb5123dd3d8770405\" data-learningcard-id=\"jp0_6S\" data-lxid=\"jp0_6S\" data-section-id=\"io1Jb30\" data-sxid=\"io1Jb30\" data-title=\"T3JhbCBjYXZpdHkg4oaSIFBhbGF0ZQ==\" id=\"L879808e013f8fa7b25b9f78225a2a41a\" data-source=\"L879808e013f8fa7b25b9f78225a2a41a\">palate</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Chronic or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"tZbXWH\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zaac4a294224f2b2a1acf64883f789cfd\" data-learningcard-id=\"sj0tbT\" data-lxid=\"sj0tbT\" data-section-id=\"R4YlQ6\" data-sxid=\"R4YlQ6\" data-title=\"U2ludXNpdGlzIOKGkiBEZWZpbml0aW9ucw==\" id=\"Lc6a530d849f98b96566bf2fc4bc6f19d\" data-source=\"Lc6a530d849f98b96566bf2fc4bc6f19d\">recurrent rhinosinusitis</span>, <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"FKWgRm0\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Gs0Bwh\" data-lxid=\"Gs0Bwh\" data-title=\"Q29tbW9uIGNvbGQ=\" id=\"L3c012bc8bf1fbe5ab5d1a5e953652345\" data-source=\"L3c012bc8bf1fbe5ab5d1a5e953652345\">nasopharyngitis</span>, and/or <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"Vm0Geg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z5c2e48c03f4f7ffb7eba5810a71d5839\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hj0KbT\" data-lxid=\"Hj0KbT\" data-title=\"RXBpc3RheGlz\" id=\"L3e2ff4d554fa9124753318ab87eea428\" data-source=\"L3e2ff4d554fa9124753318ab87eea428\">epistaxis</span></span></li>\n<li class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"Y30nSf\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QSBjb25kaXRpb24gb2YgaGF2aW5nIHVucGxlYXNhbnQgb2RvciB0byB0aGUgYnJlYXRoLiBFdGlvbG9naWVzIGluY2x1ZGUgb3JhbCBpbmZlY3Rpb25zLCBjb25zdW1wdGlvbiBvZiBjZXJ0YWluIGZvb2RzLCBnYXN0cm9lc29waGFnZWFsIHJlZmx1eCBkaXNlYXNlLCBaZW5rZXIgZGl2ZXJ0aWN1bHVtLCBhbmQgZmV0b3IgaGVwYXRpY3VzLjwvcD4=\" id=\"L0438319b65123b4f15437a069483bdc3\" data-source=\"L0438319b65123b4f15437a069483bdc3\">Halitosis</span> <span data-type=\"Reference\" data-eid=\"pCXLGZ0\" data-page=\"47–51\" data-cmt=\"\" data-ref-index=\"2\">[2]</span></li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"linksuggest\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"qx0CxR\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd56b07fa25b1c546b415c695ae197aef\" data-learningcard-id=\"Lh0wef\" data-lxid=\"Lh0wef\" data-title=\"T2JzdHJ1Y3RpdmUgc2xlZXAgYXBuZWE=\" id=\"L08ff5cb98fe6d9de8ca49a38431e0f1e\" data-source=\"L08ff5cb98fe6d9de8ca49a38431e0f1e\">Obstructive sleep apnea</span></span></span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"> (</span><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"qx0CxR\" class=\"api condensed-hidden\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd56b07fa25b1c546b415c695ae197aef\" data-learningcard-id=\"Lh0wef\" data-lxid=\"Lh0wef\" data-title=\"T2JzdHJ1Y3RpdmUgc2xlZXAgYXBuZWE=\" id=\"L0df68b004cc8e13ae0d1b1f903530a11\" data-source=\"L0df68b004cc8e13ae0d1b1f903530a11\">OSA</span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\">) </span><span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"Ed9f640fd78fb1b94658b464cc8fb83bd\"></span></span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Y428975f591c4763f371afd538b16be8e\" class=\"condensed-hidden\">Mechanical congestion of the eustachian tubes</h2>\n<ol class=\"condensed-hidden\">\n<li value=\"1\">Recurrent <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"am0QVg\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z789a45f6d93573e65d9930790c9b10fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"bF0Hg3\" data-lxid=\"bF0Hg3\" data-section-id=\"A7WRo50\" data-sxid=\"A7WRo50\" data-title=\"Q2hyb25pYyBzdXBwdXJhdGl2ZSBvdGl0aXMgbWVkaWE=\" id=\"Lb6bc90f2bc8c8f13800bdaa7ca4e05cb\" data-source=\"Lb6bc90f2bc8c8f13800bdaa7ca4e05cb\">chronic otitis media</span> <span class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"api explanation\" data-type=\"bonus\" data-content=\"\" id=\"E78f112ccccfaea704e3e34535d2f46bb\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li value=\"2\">Tympanic effusion</li>\n<li value=\"3\">\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"pcYLWL\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z3a31356a27e05a05b3786c5f01867713\" data-learningcard-id=\"6j0jYT\" data-lxid=\"6j0jYT\" data-section-id=\"OLcIB10\" data-sxid=\"OLcIB10\" data-title=\"SGVhcmluZyBsb3NzIOKGkiBPdmVydmlldw==\" id=\"L002ad8be8bd7f6342ff4cde872867ee8\" data-source=\"L002ad8be8bd7f6342ff4cde872867ee8\">Conductive hearing loss</span> → developmental disorders (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"jeW_A40\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Ze5c4d7e93247696b1b2005b16990802f\" data-learningcard-id=\"b40H3T\" data-lxid=\"b40H3T\" data-section-id=\"WuXPJ-\" data-sxid=\"WuXPJ-\" data-title=\"Q2hpbGQgZGV2ZWxvcG1lbnQgYW5kIG1pbGVzdG9uZXMg4oaSIERldmVsb3BtZW50YWwgbWlsZXN0b25lcw==\" id=\"Labfcf3cf92cbbde64a3e5edbc7fc59a3\" data-source=\"Labfcf3cf92cbbde64a3e5edbc7fc59a3\">language development</span> disorder)</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"condensed-hidden\"><span class=\"merkspruch\"><span data-phrasegroup-id=\"W8aPlm\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7c2f7198db9b555525515960ad48bd59\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"aFXQg-\" data-sxid=\"aFXQg-\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBDZWxsdWxhciBhZGFwdGF0aW9u\" id=\"L659f4787beb528532a98eddcdf10cdfa\" data-source=\"L659f4787beb528532a98eddcdf10cdfa\">Hyperplasia</span> of the pharyngeal tonsil does not itself cause symptoms. The patient only becomes symptomatic after congestion of the <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"NQ0-wf\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z93379c773fed1d12988535934bd7d0ce\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-lxid=\"ap0QLS\" data-section-id=\"Nvc-Ze0\" data-sxid=\"Nvc-Ze0\" data-title=\"QWlyd2F5cyBhbmQgbHVuZ3Mg4oaSIEdyb3NzIGFuYXRvbXk=\" id=\"Lee7cae6da00346b0dc7c37661b314d37\" data-source=\"Lee7cae6da00346b0dc7c37661b314d37\">choanae</span> and auditory tubes.</span></p>\n\n<!--no-condensed--><ul class=\"condensed-hidden\"><li>\n<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"94bNlF\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"\" id=\"L0b0be7567a24bf09b488543ccf937b91\" data-source=\"L0b0be7567a24bf09b488543ccf937b91\">Flexible nasopharyngoscopy</span> showing <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"W8aPlm\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z7c2f7198db9b555525515960ad48bd59\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-lxid=\"VP0GdT\" data-section-id=\"aFXQg-\" data-sxid=\"aFXQg-\" data-title=\"Q2VsbHVsYXIgY2hhbmdlcyBhbmQgYWRhcHRpdmUgcmVzcG9uc2VzIOKGkiBDZWxsdWxhciBhZGFwdGF0aW9u\" id=\"L08fbf76f1c9183ac0d6f68ab8936b0ae\" data-source=\"L08fbf76f1c9183ac0d6f68ab8936b0ae\">hyperplasia</span> of the adenoids</li></ul>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"condensed-hidden\">Asymptomatic adenoid vegetations do not require treatment.</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\"><span class=\"step-1-imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-1-condensed\"><span class=\"api\" data-type=\"anker\" id=\"Zf3faaddeb9cf756c21d915c0634bbc86\">Adenotonsillectomy</span></span>, or surgical excision of adenoids, is indicated for:</span><ul class=\"condensed-hidden-step1\">\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Chronic/recurrent otitis media in children</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Chronic/<span data-phrasegroup-id=\"tZbXWH\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zaac4a294224f2b2a1acf64883f789cfd\" data-learningcard-id=\"sj0tbT\" data-lxid=\"sj0tbT\" data-section-id=\"R4YlQ6\" data-sxid=\"R4YlQ6\" data-title=\"U2ludXNpdGlzIOKGkiBEZWZpbml0aW9ucw==\" id=\"L8b68aa3c3a6786a66f51bfeeff166623\" data-source=\"L8b68aa3c3a6786a66f51bfeeff166623\">recurrent sinusitis</span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"step-2-imppact2 imppact2 usmle-gs-imppact2 step-2-condensed\">Severe symptomatic nasal obstruction (e.g., <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"qx0CxR\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Zd56b07fa25b1c546b415c695ae197aef\" data-learningcard-id=\"Lh0wef\" data-lxid=\"Lh0wef\" data-title=\"T2JzdHJ1Y3RpdmUgc2xlZXAgYXBuZWE=\" id=\"L31108b63490fc177bfd1665f1edea89f\" data-source=\"L31108b63490fc177bfd1665f1edea89f\">obstructive sleep apnea</span>)</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"condensed-hidden\">Treat the underlying cause of inflammation (e.g., intranasal <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"8AbOlw\" class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-lxid=\"km0mfg\" data-section-id=\"Pq1WA30\" data-sxid=\"Pq1WA30\" data-title=\"R2x1Y29jb3J0aWNvaWRzIOKGkiBEZWZpbml0aW9u\" id=\"L992a753cba3a7e53d21323ab02239c61\" data-source=\"L992a753cba3a7e53d21323ab02239c61\">corticosteroids</span> for <span data-phrasegroup-id=\"kzbmGw\" data-type=\"bonus\" class=\"api dictionary\" data-content=\"PHA+QW4gYWJub3JtYWwgaW1tdW5vbG9naWNhbCByZXNwb25zZSB0byBhbiBvdGhlcndpc2UgaGFybWxlc3MgZW52aXJvbm1lbnRhbCBzdGltdWx1cyAoZS5nLiwgZm9vZCwgcG9sbGVuLCBhbmltYWwgZGFuZGVyKS4gTWFuaWZlc3RhdGlvbnMgaW5jbHVkZSBoaXZlcywgZWRlbWEsIHBydXJpdHVzLCBhbmQgYnJvbmNob3NwYXNtLjwvcD4=\" id=\"L9e9b3a221acb89001ab9687e04d83b46\" data-source=\"L9e9b3a221acb89001ab9687e04d83b46\">allergies</span> or <span class=\"api\" data-type=\"link\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-lxid=\"mm0VTg\" data-title=\"T3ZlcnZpZXcgb2YgYW50aWJpb3RpYyB0aGVyYXB5\" id=\"La41221b3b79cee2cb85bfb6f252822de\" data-source=\"La41221b3b79cee2cb85bfb6f252822de\">antibiotics</span> for infection)</li>\n</ul>\n            "
